    "description": "We wanted to keep this game old school. Bare minimum tutorial. Jump in and play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDemo<br />\r\nhttps://couchbrogames.itch.io/world-of-naples-lite<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWorld of Naples is a 2d platformer, speed runner, roguelike with Local PvP brawler. Up to 4 local players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n1-PVE: 20 levels total. Up to 4 players.<br />\r\n2-Local PVP: 6 arenas. Last man standing. Up to 4 players.<br />\r\n3-Keyboard, XBOX and PSP controller support.<br />\r\n4-REMOTE PLAY with your friends.<br />\r\n5-Plays nicely on Steam Deck.<br />\r\n6-Cute characters. <br />\r\n7-Challenging to hardcore gameplay.<br />\r\n8-Random quotes from great minds.<br />\r\n9-Old school. No Progress saved.<br />\r\n10-Gaming is easier with friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBetter experience with Xbox or PSP controllers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanks for reading.<br />\r\nCouch Bro Games.",
